Package org.universAAL.samples.context.reasoner.client.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    QueryCreatorFrame
    A JFrame with the basic components to build a query for the Reasoner.
    ReasoningGUI
    This is the main-frame of the reasoner-client.
    RuleCreatorFrame
    This frame is quite easy, because all have to be done to create a rule is to combine a Situation with a Query.
    SituationCreatorFrame
    Since a Situation consist of an URI for subject, predicate and object of an event-pattern there are three ComboBoxes provided to give them.
